# Incident Response - Remediator agent

NAME remediator

INPUT task

GOAL remediate """
Create a remediation plan:
- Immediate fix (stop the bleeding)
- Short-term fix (proper patch, 1-7 days)
- Long-term fix (architectural, 1-3 months)
- Verification steps for each fix
- Rollback plan if fix makes things worse
- Post-incident review action items
Include specific commands, code changes, or config updates where possible.
""" -> plan

RUN main USING remediate
